library(ggplot2)

 load("~/Desktop/FISHER SMB-A/capstone/SMB-A Capstone Project/Files 042619.RData")
 nodes <- Final_file_kNN %>% filter(Original_Gift_Amount >= 500) %>% select(Original_Gift_Source) 
nodes_01 <- nodes %>%   mutate(type = "Gift_Source")
colnames(nodes_01) <- c("name", "type")
nodes_02<- unique(nodes_01)

 nodes_city <- Final_file_kNN %>% filter(Original_Gift_Amount >= 500) %>% select(City) 
 nodes_city_01 <- nodes_city %>% mutate(type = "City")
 nodes_city_02 <- unique(nodes_city_01)
 colnames(nodes_city_02) <- c("name", "type")
 nodes_00_01 <- rbind(nodes_02,nodes_city_02 )
 nodes_00 <- unique(nodes_00_01)
nodes <- nodes_00
 

edges <- Final_file_kNN %>% filter(Original_Gift_Amount >= 500) %>% select(Original_Gift_Source, City, Original_Gift_Amount)
colnames(edges) <- c("from", "to", "weight")
edges_01 <- unique(edges)
edges_01$from <- as.character(edges_01$from)
edges_01$to <- as.character(edges_01$to)
 
edges <- edges_01

 

g <- graph_from_data_frame(edges, vertices=nodes, directed=F)
 
g1 <- as_tbl_graph(g)
g1

 ggraph(g1) +   geom_edge_link(aes(alpha = weight))  + geom_node_point(aes( color=type))

 #Eigenvector centrality- highly influential
as_tbl_graph(g1) %>% mutate(eigen=centrality_eigen()) %>% ggraph() + geom_edge_link(alpha=.1) + geom_node_point(aes(size=eigen, color=eigen)) + scale_color_continuous(guide = 'legend')
## Using `nicely` as default layout

#PageRank
as_tbl_graph(g1) %>% mutate(pagerank=centrality_pagerank()) %>% ggraph() + geom_edge_link(alpha=.1) + geom_node_point(aes(size=pagerank, color=pagerank)) +
scale_color_continuous(guide = 'legend') 
## Using `nicely` as default layout

#Closeness centrality
#Nodes that are on average close to other nodes get a high score
as_tbl_graph(g1) %>%
mutate(closeness=centrality_closeness()) %>% ggraph() + geom_edge_link() +
geom_node_point(aes(size=closeness, color=closeness)) + scale_color_continuous(guide = 'legend')
## Using `nicely` as default layout

#betweenness
as_tbl_graph(g1) %>%
mutate(betweenness=centrality_betweenness(normalized=T)) %>% ggraph() + geom_edge_link(alpha=.1) + 
  geom_node_point(aes(size=betweenness, color=betweenness)) +  scale_color_continuous(guide = 'legend') +
   geom_node_label(aes(label = name, size = .05)) 
## Using `nicely` as default layout

 as_tbl_graph(g1) %>%
mutate(betweenness=centrality_betweenness(normalized=T)) %>% ggraph() + geom_edge_link(alpha=.1) +
geom_node_point(aes(size=betweenness, color=betweenness)) + scale_color_continuous(guide = 'legend') + geom_node_text(aes(label = name, size = .05))
